OL,3,CWelsh Parliament pays tribute to
OL,4,CLabour politician Hefin David
OL,6,FMembers of the Welsh Parliament have
OL,7,Fpaid tribute to Labour politician
OL,8,FHefin David following his death last
OL,9,Fmonth.
OL,11,FWelsh First Minister Eluned Morgan
OL,12,Fdescribed Mr David as a "truly
OL,13,Fremarkable human being" at the first
OL,14,Fmeeting of the Senedd since the 47-
OL,15,Fyear-old was found dead at his home in
OL,16,FCaerphilly on August 12.
OL,18,FMr David, who had served as the Member
OL,19,Fof the Senedd for Caerphilly since
OL,20,F2016, would have turned 48 the next
OL,21,Fday.
