OL,3,CWelsh Parliament pays tribute to
OL,4,CLabour politician Hefin David
OL,6,FBaroness Morgan said: "Today, we share
OL,7,Fnot only the loss of an extraordinary
OL,8,Fcolleague and a friend, but also the
OL,9,Fprofound sorrow of losing someone who
OL,10,Floved so deeply.
OL,12,F"Thank you, Hefin, for showing us how
OL,13,Fto do this job with heart, with humour
OL,14,Fand with hope.
OL,16,F"You are loved, you are missed, and
OL,17,Fthe world is both dimmer without you
OL,18,Fand brighter for having known you.
OL,20,F"Rest in peace, friend, you'll never
OL,21,Fbe forgotten."
