OL,6,FShe said Mr David had a "heart that
OL,7,Floved fiercely" and expressed sympathy
OL,8,Ffor his partner Vikki Howells, the
OL,9,FCynon Valley MS and minister for
OL,10,Ffurther and higher education in the
OL,11,FWelsh Government.
OL,13,FDarren Millar, leader of the Welsh
OL,14,FConservatives, said: "It's difficult
OL,15,Fto put into words the shock of so
OL,16,Fsuddenly losing a colleague.
OL,18,F"Many of us here in the Senedd had
OL,19,Fknown Hefin for almost a decade.
