OL,3,CWelsh Parliament pays tribute to
OL,4,CLabour politician Hefin David
OL,6,F"Hefin was so many things to so many
OL,7,Fpeople. He was a loving son, father,
OL,8,Fbrother, partner, and friend.
OL,10,F"He was a caring boss to his staff. He
OL,11,Fwas a much-loved colleague to so many
OL,12,Fof us right across the chamber in all
OL,13,Fpolitical parties."
OL,15,FHe described Mr David as a "tireless
OL,16,Fadvocate" for Caerphilly, where
OL,17,Fcampaigning has begun before a by-
OL,18,Felection in October.
