OL,3,CWelsh Parliament pays tribute to
OL,4,CLabour politician Hefin David
OL,6,FRhun ap Iorwerth, leader of Plaid
OL,7,FCymru, said: "We remember Hefin as a
OL,8,Fpassionate and dedicated
OL,9,Fparliamentarian.
OL,11,F"He was, in many respects, everything
OL,12,Fan elected member should be, an ardent
OL,13,Fadvocate for his constituents, a
OL,14,Fcommitted campaigner for the voiceless
OL,15,Fand a free thinker never afraid to
OL,16,Fspeak his mind."
